            "Key": "FungalRat",
            "SourceString": "Weakness: Crush\r\nResistance: Stab\r\nImmune: Poison\r\n\r\nSometimes a giant rat can feast on too much magic, suffusing themselves with the energies of their environment. For the putrid rat, they can take the pestilence, rot and decay into themselves, merging with the mushrooms and poisonous fungi that they consume.\r\n\r\nThese pitiful creatures have veins that pulse with poison and upon their deaths the spores they create leave scars of rot in the world.",
